Dialogue: 0,2:07:15.00,2:07:18.80,White-双语,,0,0,0,,当当当。该起床啦囚犯。猜猜今天是什么好日子呀？\N{\fs60}Knock knock, rise and shine inmate. Guess what day it is?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:22.65,2:07:25.52,White-双语,,0,0,0,,没错哟。今天你就自由啦。\N{\fs60}That's right. As of today you're a free mare.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:30.35,2:07:33.27,White-双语,,0,0,0,,八个月过去终于重返自由，感觉肯定不错吧？\N{\fs60}It must feel nice to finally be out after eight months, huh?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:35.47,2:07:40.75,White-双语,,0,0,0,,好吧。呃，嗯，你真幸运，那个人类律师证明了你没有犯下谋杀。\N{\fs60}Right. Well, uh, you're lucky that human defense attorney proved that you didn't murder anypony.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:41.50,2:07:43.85,White-双语,,0,0,0,,如果他没成功你估计就要被送到月亮上去啦。\N{\fs60}You probably would've been banished to the moon if he hadn't.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:46.60,2:07:51.72,White-双语,,0,0,0,,至于你的随身物品…就这些。你留在法庭里的。\N{\fs60}As for your possessions...just these. You left 'em back in the courtroom.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:53.60,2:07:59.06,White-双语,,0,0,0,,那，就这样了。但在你离开前，我想问你个事。\N{\fs60}Well, this is it. But before you leave, I want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:59.70,2:08:02.77,White-双语,,0,0,0,,现在你出狱了，之后打算做什么呢？\N{\fs60}Now that you're out, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:04.02,2:08:08.40,White-双语,,0,0,0,,我将去搭救深陷冤情的小马…就如他当初搭救我一样。\N{\fs60}I'm going to help those that need it...just like he did for me.
